<h2>Welcome to LILCASOFT CMS VERSION 2.0</h2>
                    <p>+ A content management application (CMS) is the front-end user interface that allows a user, even with limited expertise, to add, modify, and remove content from a website without the intervention of a webmaster.</p>
                    <p>+ A content delivery system (CDS) compiles that information and updates the website.</p>
                    <p>+ The system is provided along with the products purchased from LilcaSoft</p>
                    <p>+ The system will automatically up to date with all new features and bug fixed if required.</p>
                    <p>+ Please use left side navigation to manipulate the content of your website.</p>
